Package com.cafean.jobstream.tracker

Class JobStreamRec

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cafean.jobstream.tracker.JobStreamRec
  • public class JobStreamRec
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class used to hold records for the JOBSTREAM Database Table. The JOBSTREAM Table contains the list of all Job Streams managed by the Tracking Server.
